                      Go West on US Airways
      Hurry! Purchase Tickets by Friday, November 30, 2001
      ----------------------------------------------------

Go west on US Airways with fares as low as $198 roundtrip for travel between most cities in the eastern U.S. and Las Vegas, Los Angeles, Orange County, Phoenix, San Diego, San Francisco or Seattle.

To take advantage of these great sale fares, book online at http://www.usairways.com/promotions/specials/east_west_sale.htm no later than November 30, 2001. 

Sale Details:

- Tickets must be purchased online at usairways.com no later than November 30, 2001
- All travel must be completed by March 14, 2002 
- Travel is not permitted December 22, 2001 
- Travel Monday-Thursday for lowest sale fares	 
- See Sale Fare Requirements below for complete details

Plus, earn double Dividend Miles on flights between now and December 15, 2001. Be sure to register for this offer before departure at http://www.usairways.com/dividendmiles/7437.htm or call 1-800-872-4738 and enter Bonus Request Number 7437.

This is just a sample of the sale fares offered.  Fares are good for travel in either direction.  For reservations and fares from your city go to http://www.usairways.com/promotions/specials/east_west_sale.htm


